text:
Is there a way to create a Share on Instagram link to put on blog post? I know the utility could be funky and I  myself can't imagine putting that as blog post share on that social media platform but I'd like to give our client the option. I figured out the code for other media platforms as such:

``` &lt;a class="share_linkedin social" title="linkedin" target="popup" onclick="window.open('<http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url={{content.absolute_url}}','LinkedIn> Share','width=600,height=600')"&gt;&lt;span class="icon-circle fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
                   &lt;a class="share_facebook social" title="facebook" target="popup" onclick="window.open('<http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u={{content.absolute_url}}','Facebook> Share','width=600,height=600')"&gt;&lt;span class="icon-circle fab fa-facebook"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;```
